      <a href="#features" class="text-sm font-medium text-surface-800/60 hover:text-surface-950 transition-colors">Features</a>
      <a href="#how-it-works" class="text-sm font-medium text-surface-800/60 hover:text-surface-950 transition-colors">How it works</a>
      <a href="#cta" class="text-sm font-medium text-surface-800/60 hover:text-surface-950 transition-colors">Pricing</a>
